<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT34">
<l>kuṟippeṉakkuk kōṭṭiyūr mēyāṉai yētta</l>
<l>kuṟippeṉakku naṉmai payakka veṟuppaṉō</l>
<l>vēṅkaṭattu mēyāṉai meyviṉaiṉō yeytāmal</l>
<l>tāṉkaṭattum taṉmaiyāṉ tāḷ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My intention is to extol [the Lord] who resides in Kōṭṭiyūr.</l>
<l>My intention is that good [should] happen [to me].</l>
<l>[So] would I loathe [the Lord] who lives in Veṅkaṭam?</l>
<l>[Would I loathe] the feet of Him whose nature is to destroy</l>
<l rend="indent">the body[-induced] karman [and] suffering</l>
<l>so that [they] do not approach [me]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
